%% Flow H — Shared-item split
flowchart TD
    WAITER[Waiter flags line as SHARED] --> FLAG[Emit bill.line.shared_flagged]
    FLAG --> BILL[Line shows shared badge on guest bill]

    BILL --> DENOM{Denominator set?}
    DENOM -->|default| ALL[All active participants]
    DENOM -->|waiter adjust| SUB[Subset e.g. 2 of 5 ate platter]

    ALL --> CALC[split.shared.calculated]
    SUB --> CALC

    CALC --> ALLOC["per_person = line_total ÷ denominator"]
    ALLOC --> ROLL[Roll into each participant subtotal]

    ROLL --> JOIN_NEW{New guest joined?}
    JOIN_NEW -->|yes| RECALC[split.shared.recalculate_requested]
    RECALC --> PROMPT[Staff or guest confirm recalc]
    PROMPT --> CALC

    JOIN_NEW -->|no| PAY[Continue to tip/checkout]

    subgraph Example["Numeric example"]
        EX1["Platter €25.00 ÷ 5 guests = €5.00 each"]
    end

    style WAITER fill:#fc9
    style PAY fill:#9cf
